<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <div class="header-container">
    <div class="title-section">
      <h1>Hello</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-image">
      <img src="/images/pic.jpg" alt="Profile picture" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>About Me</h2>
  <p>
    I am an academic researcher interested in interdisciplinary work in Human-Centered Computing,
    especially at the intersection of machine learning and ethics, machine behavior, and quantitative
    empirical legal studies.
  </p>
  <p>
    Currently, I am a PhD Candidate in the Department of Informatics at the Pontifical Catholic
    University of Rio de Janeiro (PUC-Rio). I also conduct research at the Center for Technology and
    Society at FGV Direito Rio.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can find my <a href="/publications/">Publications</a> and <a href="/courses/">Course Materials</a> on their respective pages.
  </p>

  <h2>Research Interests</h2>
  <p>My research focuses on:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Ethical aspects of Machine Learning development and deployment</li>
    <li>Machine psychology</li>
    <li>Data-driven empirical legal studies</li>
    <li>Moral evaluation of Large Language Models</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Teaching</h2>
  <p>I teach the following undergraduate courses at FGV Direito Rio undergraduate program:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Programming for Lawyers</li>
    <li>Legal Data Science</li>
  </ul>

